episodes.title: #82 Breaking Free
episodes.description: Episode #82 Breaking Free Nick sits down with Amber Powers who has a tremendous story of being raised in a cult and the had the ability to Break Free from the control and captivity associated with that way of life. You'll hear how she has even lost family members in the Jonestown Massacre. Most of all you hear how she had resilience to not conform and her willingness to help others.
